achiever.brings: a steady drive to keep moving and accomplishing
achiever.canOverdo: pushing too hard or finding it difficult to switch off

activator.brings: energy that turns ideas into action
activator.canOverdo: moving before others are ready or before thinking is complete

adaptability.brings: an ability to stay open and responsive as things shift

analytical.brings: clarity through careful thinking and evaluation

arranger.brings: an ability to organise people and resources effectively

belief.brings: a strong moral compass and sense of why
belief.canOverdo: appearing inflexible when values are challenged

command.brings: confidence and presence in moments of uncertainty
command.canOverdo: coming across as forceful or intimidating

communication.brings: an ability to give shape and meaning through language
communication.canOverdo: talking when listening would serve better

competition.canOverdo: focusing too much on winning rather than learning

connectedness.brings: a sense of connection between people and events
connectedness.canOverdo: over-attributing meaning or avoiding difficult choices

consistency.brings: a pull towards clarity, fairness, and dependable ways of working
consistency.canOverdo: becoming rigid or frustrated by exceptions

context.brings: perspective by grounding decisions in what has gone before
context.canOverdo: staying rooted in the past when change is needed

deliberative.brings: a thoughtful and cautious approach to decisions

developer.brings: belief in people and patience with development
developer.canOverdo: investing in growth when it may not be wanted

discipline.brings: reliability and order through well-designed routines
discipline.canOverdo: struggling when things feel messy or unplanned

empathy.brings: an intuitive sense of what others are feeling
empathy.canOverdo: absorbing emotions that are not theirs to carry

focus.brings: the ability to concentrate energy on what matters most
focus.canOverdo: ignoring useful distractions or alternative ideas

futuristic.brings: hope and inspiration through a compelling view of the future

harmony.brings: a calming influence that reduces unnecessary conflict
harmony.canOverdo: avoiding healthy debate or difficult conversations

ideation.canOverdo: generating ideas without moving to action

includer.brings: a sense of welcome and inclusion

individualization.brings: insight into what makes each person distinct

input.brings: a rich store of knowledge and resources

intellection.brings: depth and insight through careful reflection
intellection.canOverdo: withdrawing into thinking at the expense of action

learner.brings: energy and enthusiasm for growth and development
learner.canOverdo: staying in learning mode instead of applying knowledge

maximizer.brings: a focus on making good things great
maximizer.canOverdo: neglecting what is adequate but necessary

relator.canOverdo: appearing reserved or slow to open up

responsibility.canOverdo: taking on too much or struggling to say no

restorative.brings: confidence in tackling and resolving problems
restorative.canOverdo: focusing on problems rather than possibilities

selfassurance.brings: a calm certainty in their own judgement

significance.brings: a desire to do work that truly matters

strategic.brings: clarity through seeing pathways and possibilities
strategic.canOverdo: staying in planning rather than execution
